{"tid":2088072,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"張曉明怒問：制裁中方官員？ 有無搞錯 關你咩事！","createTime":"2020-07-01T03:28:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-01T03:57:49.000Z","uid":7542,"like":9,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"0f9174762bc9df32f43bf90bd9c2ac7fddca0377","tid":2088072,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T03:28:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n港澳辦常務副主任張曉明表示，全國人大訂立《港區國安法》沒有超出一國兩制框架。他認為，香港已出現偏離一國兩制軌道及挑戰相關底線的現象，認為立法在一定程度上要「糾偏」，往「一國」拉進一些，強調是要堅持完善、並非要改變「一國兩制」。張曉明說，有其他國家的政客說，中國要搞一國一制，他說如果是這樣，事情就簡單得多，中央可以直接把內地刑法適用於香港，無需要花這麼大周章，為香港度身訂做一部國安法。他指出，中央一直強調要全面準確貫切一國兩制方針，但香港及國際上都有人把一國兩制的「經」念歪，每當中央依法行使某些權利時，西方都有人出來指責說是破壞一國兩制，認為好像香港甚麼事情中央都不能管，反而他們能指手劃腳。他反問，中央怎能坐視不理，相信沒有人比中央對一國兩制有定義權。對於有國家提出，要對中方官員實行嚴厲制裁，張曉明認為，是強盜邏輯，強調《港區國安法》完全是中國內政，西方國家憑甚麼可以動粗，又以廣東話說「有無搞錯、關你咩事」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1535126-20200701.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1535126-20200701.htm&d=oa%2BbSijZO%2BDWYSsAyiffbsF4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=a871763c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1535126-20200701.htm&h=172db379\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1535126-20200701.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/i7ZF_dgqG3s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fi7ZF_dgqG3s&d=oa%2BbSijZO%2BDWYSsAyiffbsF4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=fae7dc1a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/i7ZF_dgqG3s</a>"},{"pid":"e4cce14440eccd36570ad6eb021d3632d0f6a84e","tid":2088072,"uid":19552,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T03:29:59.000Z","msg":"下次講粗口 關你撚事嘛"},{"pid":"6d4059920baec78756db05c23f7cc657a64fbe26","tid":2088072,"uid":352873,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T03:30:45.000Z","msg":"好型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1037340ad38643009b88e076a5e18f303d18d2f5","tid":2088072,"uid":49336,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T03:31:53.000Z","msg":"即時翻譯： 要搞搞駱惠寧關我乜事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dc1c2eba06956d768734c54c63ddd12f4747ac5","tid":2088072,"uid":209024,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T03:31:59.000Z","msg":"覺得對你無影響 咪唔好出聲lor"},{"pid":"9b41d45d0e3f50ad0461238710c27a8d24da9dc0","tid":2088072,"uid":353256,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T03:32:21.000Z","msg":"點解所羅門講on9又係講廣東話，張曉明又係講廣東話，張曉明硬係柒過人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5be7cd8494fe6c09bac02d4c9b905d814bc8bf06","tid":2088072,"uid":304769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T03:34:59.000Z","msg":"今年七一要加主題：<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n寧願最後不得善終<br />\n也不考慮含淚折衷<br />\n<br />\n我要美國做野，無懼與支共同歸於盡，寧死捍衛自由民主</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n認同就拎張紙舉比美國睇，咪比條廢老Martin Lee騎劫我地，搞到美國以為我地驚攬炒而唔做野<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黃世澤出左香港自治法篤灰指南，好有用，大家入去睇</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/s6o2r5DkT-w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fs6o2r5DkT-w&d=oa%2BbSijZO%2BDWYSsAyiffbsF4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=2729d5f1\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/s6o2r5DkT-w</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n借個位<br />\n正視聽：若抗爭方向不隨局勢改變，只會無謂地損兵折將<br />\n香港街頭抗爭目標，亦都係街頭抗爭最大效果；&ldquo;攬炒&rdquo;已經達到，今次搞蟈安法其實仲攬炒過上年出老解。<br />\n宜家<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">跟著落黎就係引導全球政府同議會（尤其美國）對付支那以及滅共</span></strong>，所以大家重點應該著眼帶出清晰民意授權比各國政府做野，畫面靚+全球廣泛報導（類似反蟈安法銅鑼灣自由行）係最理想，用選票帶出民意亦十分重要。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大家要小心五毛、熱普城共諜放負風向：美國唔會幫我地（舊年年尾）-》英國係廢國無用架（今年年頭）-》歐盟奶共唔會幫我地、美國制裁無用（宜家）</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n大家要記住，香港生路只有一條：救香港人+攬炒促進支爆+重建香港。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">沒有支爆，香港獨立或者歸英等重建方案全部都係痴人說夢。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n未來幾個月至支共瓦解期間大家要做嘅事：1.<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">走資</span></strong>2.全球救生艇<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">救手足加有細路既黃絲家庭</span></strong>（細路是重點，香港未來棟樑，正如今時今日d前線義士，咪比佢地洗腦變小糞紅，否則香港係真正玩完）3.比足夠<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">民意授權，敦促美國以至各國停止外匯流入香港</span></strong>，包括但不限於：禁止美國個人或公司投資港股、債券，暫停接受香港用美元結算等等4.最後就真係等<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>支那自己爆</strong></span>"},{"pid":"814e34550929c7214a8a75a8dd521e8b923fc46a","tid":2088072,"uid":224533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T03:37:00.000Z","msg":"西方： what 7 you saying"},{"pid":"cf67fb88c87c0f9f5e3f192ebe96f87697734e5f","tid":2088072,"uid":189,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T03:37:39.000Z","msg":"同鬼佬講點解唔係講英文"},{"pid":"f51852d09b81c58877c21e1de9d294993505c0b4","tid":2088072,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b41d45d0e3f50ad0461238710c27a8d24da9dc0","tid":2088072,"uid":353256,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T03:32:21.000Z","msg":"點解所羅門講on9又係講廣東話，張曉明又係講廣東話，張曉明硬係柒過人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T03:38:05.000Z","msg":"有無片"},{"pid":"562c38ad403844ba8468cc77b8c09e287941e434","tid":2088072,"uid":177168,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T03:38:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tPBnz2s.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtPBnz2s.gif&h=dbacc198&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b4daa545ee4e90df7983d6456ad61a0e3ee6a907","tid":2088072,"uid":259565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T03:39:5