2020-07-01T03:48:56.000Z","msg":"我已經降職，仲要制裁我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71e39698d337126e4f20b5d6d8ac66b52055e3ac","tid":2088072,"uid":244818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T03:51:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2744b7fd5f07a1aaef15b7771ed818ccb901ce6","tid":2088072,"uid":42548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T03:55:31.000Z","msg":"關仔閪事死鞋秋面佬，被人降職中聯辦呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39709097c9cd8cfbfa2db400525c25e252727f7e","tid":2088072,"uid":110579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T03:55:50.000Z","msg":"佢所謂度身訂造其實冇講錯<br />\n但冇可能係從香港人角度出發<br />\n因爲佢要保住一國兩制呢個貞節牌坊繼續掠晒外國佬錢嘛，同時間又要開始壓制反對聲音，事實上香港問題國際關注程度已經超出所有人預期包括共匪<br />\n事成定事敗未有最後答案咁解"},{"pid":"309de78a3b9e8bf2b6b38a2a77db27758d038ed0","tid":2088072,"uid":51583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T03:57:49.000Z","msg":"地球上的事就是地球人的事"}]}